    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed. The team noted that all assessed factors fell below required levels and six factors remain unassessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5, but concluded that the documented gaps were acceptable given the exploratory nature of the submission stage. No applicability constraint or operating envelope was defined for the ContextOfUse, leaving the valid range of model use unspecified.",
